room_title: Escape room "The Estate" by Trapped in Tahoe in South Lake Tahoe
room_address: 3320 Sandy Way, Unit 1, South Lake Tahoe, CA 96150
room_description: You have been hired to help renovate an old mansion. It has been in the owner's family for generations and is quite notorious in town. Legend says there is bad blood in this house. And the ghosts that haunt it thirst for revenge. But a few spooky stories aren't enough to stop you and your crew from taking on a job that pays three times what anyone else will. After all..... You ain't afraid of no ghost!
